		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</em></p><p><em>This brass bottle exhales a roiling bank of smoke whenever it is opened.</em></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - Self</p><p><strong>Utility</strong></p><p>Open or close the bottle.</p><ul><li><p>Opening the bottle releases thick smoke that fills a 60 ft Emanation originating from the bottle; the area is &amp;Reference[HeavilyObscured].</p></li><li><p>Each minute the bottle remains open, the Emanation expands by 10 feet, to a maximum radius of 120 feet.</p></li><li><p>Closing the bottle fixes the cloud in place; it disperses after 10 minutes or in 1 minute if subjected to a strong wind (such as <em>Gust of Wind</em>).</p></li></ul><section id=\"foundry-secret-1\" class=\"secret\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The scaling slider of the <strong>Open Bottle</strong> activity controls the size of the created Emanation from 60 feet at scaling value 1 to 120 feet at scaling value 7 (increments of 10 feet).</p></section>",
